lson of Tillyorn]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[University of Aberdeen|Chancellor of the University of Aberdeen]]|years= 2013\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Camilla, Duchess of Cornwall}}\n{{Navboxes\n|list={{British princesses by marriage}}\n{{UK Order of Precedence (Ladies)}}\n{{Princesses of Wales}}\n{{Duchesses of Rothesay}}\n{{University of Aberdeen}}\n}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n{{Portal bar|Biography|Monarchy|Royalty|London|England}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cornwall, Camilla, Duchess of}}\n[[Category:1947 births]]\n[[Category:Anti-poverty advocates]]\n[[Category:British Anglicans]]\n[[Category:British countesses]]\n[[Category:British duchesses by marriage]]\n[[Category:British health activists]]\n[[Category:Wives of British princes]]\n[[Category:British racehorse owners and breeders]]\n[[Category:British women activists]]\n[[Category:Chancellors of the University of Aberdeen]]\n[[Category:Companions of the Star of Melanesia]]\n[[Category:Cubitt family]]\n[[Category:Dames Grand Cross of the Royal Victorian Order]]\n[[Category:Duchesses of Rothesay]]\n[[Category:Edmonstone family]]\n[[Category:Grand Cross of the National Order of Merit (France)]]\n[[Category:Honorary air commodores]]\n[[Category:House of Windsor]]\n[[Category:Keppel family]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Members of the Privy Council of the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:Mistresses of British royalty]]\n[[Category:Mountbatten-Windsor family]]\n[[Category:Parker family]]\n[[Category:People educated at Queen's Gate School]]\n[[Category:People educated at the University of London Institute in Paris]]\n[[Category:People from East Sussex]]\n[[Category:People from South Kensington]]\n[[Category:People of United Empire Loyalist descent]]\n[[Category:Patrons of schools]]\n[[Category:Princesses of Wales]]\n[[Category:Sexual abuse victim advocates]]\n[[Category:Shand family|Camilla]]\n[[Category:The Queen's Own Rifles of Canada]]\n", "name_user": "GiantSnowman", "label": "safe", "comment": "date format